It is very easy to assemble this office desk with filing cabinet, without much of hassle. Tribesigns provides 12 MONTHS warranty and 24 hours customer service for any problem. Feel free to get this desk for your home office!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 13, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is a very nice desk for the price! Great color and structure, seems very solid and doesn't take up much space. Was fairly simple to put together and I love the option of the cabinet going on either side. The drawers have a nice depth to them but the top is just a little less spacious than I thought but it works. My only minor complaint would be the drawers. They are not on a track, the drawers themselves slide on the metal frame, and because of this they are sometimes a little difficult to open and close smoothly and sometimes stick and drag. But overall I would definitely recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Impressed with the quality and ease of assembly.
reviews.reviewText: While the package was quite heavy and the instructions stated that two people should assemble, I did assembly by myself and it was easy. Like all furniture assembly, look at the instructions carefully and lay the parts out so you can access them easily. The quality is very good and I love the appearance. A great price and it fits my Canon printer perfectly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Nice computer desk big enough for your computer and other stuff, very sturdy wish the printer part was a little bigger.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this desk
reviews.reviewText: Good price, really sturdy, easy to put together. It was easier to put together with two people but I’m a novice on putting stuff together and I still found it easy. And I really love it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect little desk
reviews.reviewText: Even though I found the assembly a little challenging, once I got it together, I love it. The reversible drawers are convenient, the desk is very sturdy, the spacious drawers slide easily and it is perfect for small spaces. Great design, does not look cheap, and very good value. The Allen key supplied was a tad small. I really recommend this desk.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect kid desk that is perfect for Grown-up needs
reviews.reviewText: This lovely desk came in a lot of pieces, but it's pretty straight-forward to put together. All pieces were there. It's stable and study and worth way more than the price. I do wish the drawers came on metal tracks for easy sliding, but I'll overlook it given how much I love the rest of it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It fit in the small area we had.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy but small
reviews.reviewText: This unit was easy to assemble, but once together seemed a little bit small. The drawers run on square metal tubing. This makes the drawers sturdy, but not easy to open and close. We purchased two of these so that we could install them together, one installed left and the other installed right for a his and hers work area.
